                                    {
                                        "type": "paragraph",
                                        "inlines": [
                                            {
                                                "text": "在“Car & Vehicle Electronics”品类中长期排名前列，用户评价呈现两极分化。"
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    }
                                ],
                                "align": "center"
                            },
                            {
                                "blocks": [
